==Introduction==
艦隊の航空偵察の主役として、戦いの前半期では幅広い局面で活躍した「零式水上偵察機」。<br>
戦艦や巡洋艦、水上機母艦などに搭載され、三座を活かして艦隊の「目」としての索敵任務に務めました。<br>
本機は、哨戒性能等を強化した同機の改良後期型です。

''A "Type 0 Reconnaissance Seaplane" that played a large role as the fleets' aerial scout during various stages in the first half of the war.''<br>
''It was carried by battleships, cruisers and seaplane tenders among other ships and served as the "eye" of the fleet during reconnaissance missions by capitalising on its three seats.''<br>
''This plane is an improved model that received modifications to its patrolling capabilities etc.''

